{"tid":709357,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女童夢話「不要碰我！」　家長揪出教會狼師","createTime":"2018-06-20T02:43:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T02:51:02.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d0919d8792864d553fcb839988f0225bbb075a16","tid":709357,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:43:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">新北</span></ins></strong>10歲女童參加林口某教會的課輔活動，遭課輔老師猥褻，造成心理陰影常做惡夢。家屬察覺有異，詢問後揪出狼師，新北地院昨依強制猥褻罪判狼師2年8月徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n今日出版的《聯合報》報導，判決指出，該名狼師去年初將被害女童帶到教會廚房後，隔著衣褲撫摸女童下體。去年9月更得寸進尺，一小時內3度將手伸進女童內褲和上衣，撫摸下體、胸部。女童半夜常做惡夢，大叫「不要碰我」，家長追問才揭狼師獸行。<br />\n<br />\n法官考量他當庭認錯並表示極度後悔，且與女童達成和解，依2次強制猥褻罪，合併應執行2年8月有期徒刑。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180620/1376297/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180620%2F1376297%2F&d=4p24QOPJguqBpXfAtBOJjIS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=713202cb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20180620%2F1376297%2F&h=124e89c9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20180620/1376297/</a>"},{"pid":"f23b8205d5edbe742d86584794f450749e25dd1e","tid":709357,"uid":12757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"到底新北呢個地方 點解捉極都仲咁多風化案既<br />\n係咪刑罰好輕？"},{"pid":"3177f27d6ca196281776f14b869a933954ea6e78","tid":709357,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f23b8205d5edbe742d86584794f450749e25dd1e","tid":709357,"uid":12757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:46:02.000Z","msg":"到底新北呢個地方 點解捉極都仲咁多風化案既<br />\n係咪刑罰好輕？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T02:47:21.000Z","msg":"衰老強判三年到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a96a1c57822a65adf8003f0c6bd061e853a1ba0","tid":709357,"uid":12757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"p